@node "Installation" "Installation"
               @{b}@{fg highlight}Installation@{ub}@{fg text}
               @{b}@{u}@{fg shadow}@{bg shine}============@{ub}@{uu}@{fg text}@{bg back}

   Just copy the whole drawer to a location in your harddrive.
   Before YAAV is run you MUST configure it by changing the tooltypes. This can be done by clicking on
the YAAV icon and then pressing @{i}RightAmiga-I.@{ui}
