@node "ToolTypes" "ToolTypes"
               @{b}@{fg highlight}YAAV ToolTypes@{ub}@{fg text}
               @{b}@{u}@{fg shadow}@{bg shine}==============@{ub}@{uu}@{fg text}@{bg back}

YAAV accepts the following tooltypes to set its preferences:

   @{b}AUTODOCS=@{i}@{ub}path_name@{ui}   Set the directory where your Autodocs reside.
                        Default is DOCS:

   @{b}INCLUDES=@{i}@{ub}path_name@{ui}   Set the directory where your Includes reside.
                        Default is INCLUDE:

   @{b}FD=@{i}@{ub}path_name @{ui}        Set the directory where your .fd files reside.
                        Default is FD:

   @{b}FONTNAME=@{i}@{ub}font_name@{ui}   Set viewing font name (including the .font extension!).
                        Default is topaz.

   @{b}FONTSIZE=@{i}@{ub}font_size@{ui}   Set the viewing font size. Default is 8
@endnode

